cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.SY, cs.PF 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with power consumption in cellular networks, which is a networking issue. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also likely as the paper uses mathematical expressions to model power consumption. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possibility as the paper discusses radio propagation environments, which can affect multimedia transmission. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper discusses cell selection and handoff algorithms, which are part of the control system of cellular networks. 
- cs.PF (Performance) is a possibility as the paper discusses the performance of cellular networks in terms of power consumption.
